"title": "5015: heart, and Holy Spirit",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5015",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>The Holy Spirit comes to dwell within believers, renewing them and directing their hearts towards a greater love for God.</p>\n<h2>The renewal of the heart by the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:10\">PSA 51:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek36:26\">EZK 36:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:12-Ps51:17\">PSA 51:12–51:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer24:7\">JER 24:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ezek18:31\">EZK 18:31</a></p>\n<h2>The heart as the residence of the Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:9\">ROM 8:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John7:37-John7:39\">JHN 7:37–7:39</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:5\">ROM 5:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor1:22\">2CO 1:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:6\">GAL 4:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:16-Eph3:17\">EPH 3:16–3:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:27\">COL 1:27</a></p>\n<h2>The heart bears the fruit of the Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:22-Gal5:23\">GAL 5:22–5:23</a></strong></p>\n<h3>Love for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark12:30\">MRK 12:30</a></strong> parallels <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt22:37\">MAT 22:37</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:27\">LUK 10:27</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod25:2\">EXO 25:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:5\">DEU 6:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut11:13\">DEU 11:13</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:6\">DEU 30:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs15:14\">1KI 15:14</a></p>\n<h3>Faithfulness to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps44:18\">PSA 44:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs2:4\">1KI 2:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:18\">1CH 29:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh9:8\">NEH 9:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts11:23\">ACT 11:23</a></p>\n<h2>Other results of the Holy Spirit's indwelling of the heart</h2>\n<h3>Heartfelt worship of God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col3:16\">COL 3:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:1\">1SA 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr11:16\">2CH 11:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr29:31\">2CH 29:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job11:13\">JOB 11:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:1\">PSA 9:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:21\">PSA 33:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps86:12\">PSA 86:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps138:1\">PSA 138:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom15:6\">ROM 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:18-Eph5:19\">EPH 5:18–5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:3\">PHP 3:3</a></p>\n<h3>Heartfelt prayer to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:145\">PSA 119:145</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen24:45\">GEN 24:45</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam1:13\">1SA 1:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr22:19\">1CH 22:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps21:2\">PSA 21:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps27:8\">PSA 27:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:2\">PSA 84:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:26-Rom8:27\">ROM 8:26–8:27</a></p>\n<h3>Wholehearted obedience to God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:34\">PSA 119:34</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut26:16\">DEU 26:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:14-Deut30:17\">DEU 30:14–30:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:46\">DEU 32:46</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs14:8\">1KI 14:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:3\">2KI 23:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs23:25\">2KI 23:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Neh2:12\">NEH 2:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps40:8\">PSA 40:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:2\">PSA 119:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:69\">PSA 119:69</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:112\">PSA 119:112</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:17\">ROM 6:17</a></p>\n<h3>Wholehearted trust in God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5-Prov3:6\">PRO 3:5–3:6</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps62:8\">PSA 62:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark11:23\">MRK 11:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke24:25\">LUK 24:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:22\">HEB 10:22</a></p>\n<h3>Wholehearted service for God</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:9\">ROM 1:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut10:12\">DEU 10:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh22:5\">JOS 22:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:20\">1SA 12:20</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:24\">1SA 12:24</a></p>",
